    },
    {
      "text": "Daedalian Opus (冒険!パズルロード, Bōken! Pazuru Rōdo; Adventure! Puzzle Road) is a puzzle video game for the Game Boy that was released in 1990, in July. It was developed and published by Vic Tokai.",
